<view class="page">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="title-main">星盘</view>
    <view class="title-sub">公历生日 → 12 星座 (不严守不卖)</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="title-sub">您的公历生日</view>
    <picker mode="date" value="{{birthDate}}" bindchange="onPickDate" start="1940-01-01" end="2026-12-31">
      <view class="picker-view">公历生日 · {{birthDate || '轻触选择'}}</view>
    </picker>
    <view class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: 24rpx;" bindtap="onSubmit">看星盘</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{result}}">
    <view class="card">
      <view class="title-sub">{{result.zodiac.name}}</view>
      <view class="text-body" style="margin-top: 12rpx; font-size: 24rpx; color: #a8a29e;">
        {{result.zodiac.dateRange}} · {{result.zodiac.element}} · {{result.zodiac.trait}}
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card">
      <view class="title-sub">调性解读</view>
      <view class="text-body" style="margin-top: 12rpx; color: #4a7c59;">
        {{result.zodiac.reading}}
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card">
      <view class="title-sub">推荐经文 (3 篇)</view>
      <view class="text-body" wx:for="{{result.jingwen}}" wx:key="id" wx:for-item="j" style="margin-top: 12rpx;">
        • {{j.source}} · {{j.title}}
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card">
      <view class="title-sub">推荐汤品 (3 款)</view>
      <view class="text-body" wx:for="{{result.soups}}" wx:key="id" wx:for-item="s" style="margin-top: 12rpx;">
        • {{s.name}} — {{s.desc}}
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="compliance-bar">
    ✦ 星盘为西方占星文化, 仅供参考, 不构成人生指引。悦济不卖占星服务。
  </view>
</view>
